Date: Sat, 9 May 2026 15:33:31 +0100
Subject: [PATCH] feat: Add support for setting the primary monitor (#898)

* Add support for setting the primary monitor

* Switch from json to local keyfile to save cached monitor data

* Restructure displays page - include button to run wdisplays

* Cleanup lamda usage

* Remove unneeded vapi files

* Reset submodule back to main
